ys what steamboats consumed week doing towing fleets killed through freight traffic dragging six seven steamer loads stuff river time expense trivial steamboat competition question freight passenger way traffic remains steamers hands along two thousand miles river between st paul new orleans two three close corporations well fortified capital able thoroughly business like management system these make sufficiency money what left once prodigious steamboating industry suppose st louis new orleans suffered materially change alas wood yard man used fringe river all way his close ranked merchandise stretched one city other along banks sold uncountable cords every year cash nail all scattering boats left burn coal now seldomest spectacle mississippi day wood pile where now once wood yard man 23 traveling incognito idea tarry while every town between st louis new orleans necessary go place place short packet lines easy plan make been easy one follow twenty years ago now there wide intervals between boats these days wanted begin interesting old french settlements st genevieve kaskaskia sixty miles below st louis there only one boat advertised section grand tower packet still one boat enough went look venerable rack heap fraud boot playing herself personal property whereas good honest dirt thickly caked all righteously taxable real estate there places new england where hurricane deck worth hundred fifty dollars acre soil forecastle quite good new crop wheat already springing cracks protected places companionway dry sandy character been well suited grapes southern exposure little subsoiling soil boiler deck thin rocky good enough grazing purposes colored boy watch here nobody else visible gathered calm craft go advertised if got trip if didn t get wait got any trip bless no boss ain t unloadened yit only come dis mawnin uncertain when might get trip thought might morrow maybe next day answer all give novelty sailing river farm one more arrow quiver vicksburg packet gold dust l