ely died fortress arberg where been confined many years being said concerned conspiracy berne memorial judicious critique extensive ridiculous plan fortification which been adopted geneva though censured every person judgment art who unacquainted secret motives council execution magnificent enterprise monsieur de micheli who been excluded committee fortification having condemned plan thought citizen member two hundred might give his advice large therefore memorial which imprudent enough printed though never published having only those copies struck off which meant two hundred which all intercepted post house order senate grand council geneva december 1728 pronounced paper highly disrespectful councils injurious committee fortification found memorial among uncle s papers answer been ordered make took both soon after left place survey yet remained good terms counsellor de coccelli who management some time after director custom house entreated stand godfather his child madam coccelli who godmother proud being placed such terms equality counsellor wished assume importance show myself worthy honor full idea thought nothing better show micheli s memorial which really scarce piece prove connected people consequence geneva who intrusted secrets state yet kind reserve which should find difficult account show uncle s answer perhaps because manuscript nothing less print worthy approach counsellor understood however well importance paper which folly put his hands never after get possession being convinced every effort purpose ineffectual made merit forbearance transforming theft present made no doubt writing more curious however useful answered his purpose court turin where probably took care reimbursed some way other expense which acquisition might supposed cost happily all future contingencies least probable ever king sardina should besiege geneva event absolutely impossible shall ever reproach foolish vanity having been means pointing greatest defects city its most ancient e