es upwards thousand livres forty pounds well epinay chevrette during five six years most assiduous there these expenses inevitable man like who knows how provide anything himself cannot support sight lackey who grumbles serves sour look madam dupin even where one family whose house rendered many services servants never received theirs money course time necessary renounce these little liberalities which situation no longer permitted bestow felt still more severely inconvenience associating people situation different own manner life been taste should been consoled heavy expense which dedicated pleasures ruin myself same time fatigued mind insupportable felt weight profiting interval liberty determined perpetuate entirely renounce great companies composition books all literary concerns remainder days confine myself narrow peaceful sphere which felt born move produce letter d alembert new elosia little improved state finances which been considerably exhausted hermitage emilius which after finished eloisa given great application forwardness produce less sum which already possession intended place money such manner produce little annual income which copying might sufficient wants without writing any more two other works upon stocks first these institutions politiques examined state work found required several years labor courage enough continue wait until finished before carried intentions execution therefore laying book aside determined take all burn rest continuing zeal without interrupting emilius finished contrat social dictionary music now remained mechanical might taken any time object entirely pecuniary reserved myself liberty laying aside finishing ease according other resources collected should render necessary superfluous respect morale sensitive which made nothing more sketch entirely gave last project if found entirely without copying removing paris where affluence visitors rendered housekeeping expensive deprived time should turned advantage provide prevent r