ant course going land little island where walked hour two laid myself grass summit hill there satiate myself pleasure admiring lake its environs examine dissect all herbs within reach like another robinson crusoe built myself imaginary place residence island became very much attached eminence when brought theresa wife receiver sisters walk there how proud pilot guide took there rabbits stock another source pleasure jean jacques these animals rendered island still more interesting afterwards went more frequently greater pleasure observe progress new inhabitants these amusements added one which recalled recollection delightful life led charmettes which season particularly invited assisting rustic labors gathering roots fruits which theresa made pleasure partake wife receiver his family remember bernois one m kirkeberguer coming see found perched upon tree sack fastened waist already full apples stir branch which stood sorry caught similar situations hoped people berne witnesses employment leisure no longer think disturbing tranquillity leave peace solitude should preferred being confined there desire rendered continuation repose more certain another declaration upon which am previously certain incredulity many readers who obstinately continue judge themselves although cannot seen course life thousand internal affections which bore no resemblance any theirs what still more extraordinary refuse every sentiment good indifferent which constantly ready attribute such bad ones cannot enter heart man case find easy set opposition nature make such monster cannot reality exist nothing absurd appears incredible moment tendency blacken nothing least extraordinary seems possible if tends honor notwithstanding what may think say still continue faithfully state what j j rousseau thought without explaining justifying singularity his sentiments ideas endeavoring discover whether others thought became delighted island st peter residence there agreeable concentrating all desires within