idden no more week before month able take road again good heart all time alan leave though often pressed indeed his foolhardiness staying common subject outcry two three friends let secret hid day hole braes little wood night when coast clear come house visit need say if pleased see mrs maclaren hostess thought nothing good enough such guest duncan dhu which name host pair pipes his house much lover music time recovery quite festival commonly turned night day soldiers let us although once party two companies some dragoons went bottom valley where see through window lay bed what much more astonishing no magistrate came near there no question put whence came whither going time excitement free all inquiry though lain desert yet presence known before left all people balquhidder adjacent parts many coming house visits these after custom country spreading news among neighbours bills too now been printed there one pinned near foot bed where read own very flattering portrait larger characters amount blood money been set upon life duncan dhu rest knew come there alan s company entertained no doubt who many others must guess though changed clothes change age person lowland boys eighteen rife these parts world above all time fail put one thing another connect bill least other folk keep secret among two three near friends somehow leaks among these clansmen told whole countryside keep century there one thing happened worth narrating visit robin oig one sons notorious rob roy sought upon all sides charge carrying young woman balfron marrying alleged force yet stepped balquhidder like gentleman his own walled policy who shot james maclaren plough stilts quarrel never satisfied yet walked house his blood enemies rider 30 might public inn 30 commercial traveller duncan time pass word who looked one another concern should understand close upon time alan s coming two little likely agree yet if sent word sought make signal sure arouse suspicion man dark cloud macgregor came great show 